            <title><![CDATA[RaaS, Ransomware as a Service]]></title>
            <link>https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/security/raas/</link>
            <guid>https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/security/raas/</guid>
            <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 12:52:18 GMT</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[Ransomware as a Service]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_n3DU" id="랜섬웨어의-개념">랜섬웨어의 개념<a class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to heading" title="Direct link to heading" href="https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/security/raas/#%EB%9E%9C%EC%84%AC%EC%9B%A8%EC%96%B4%EC%9D%98-%EA%B0%9C%EB%85%90">​</a></h2>
<ul>
<li>몸값(Ransome)과 소프트웨어의 합성어로 시스템을 감염시커 사용 불가능한 샅애로 만들거나, 데이터를 암호화해 사용할 수 없게한 뒤 금전을 요구하는 악성프로그램</li>
<li>다크웹 등 익명 N/W를 통해 누구나 랜섬웨어를 의뢰, 구매하여 공격에 활용할 수 있는 RaaS 형태로 진화</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_n3DU" id="raas의-매커니즘-공격절차-대응방안">RaaS의 매커니즘, 공격절차, 대응방안<a class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to heading" title="Direct link to heading" href="https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/security/raas/#raas%EC%9D%98-%EB%A7%A4%EC%BB%A4%EB%8B%88%EC%A6%98-%EA%B3%B5%EA%B2%A9%EC%A0%88%EC%B0%A8-%EB%8C%80%EC%9D%91%EB%B0%A9%EC%95%88">​</a></h2>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_n3DU" id="raas의-매커니즘">RaaS의 매커니즘<a class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to heading" title="Direct link to heading" href="https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/security/raas/#raas%EC%9D%98-%EB%A7%A4%EC%BB%A4%EB%8B%88%EC%A6%98">​</a></h3>
]]></content:encoded>
